  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Way Of Heaven
---
\"Excellent!" said Confucius, and went to see Lao Tan, but Lao Tan would
not give permission. Thereupon Confucius unwrapped his Twelve Classics
and began expounding them. Halfway through the exposition, Lao Tan
said, "This will take forever! Just let me hear the gist of the thing"
